snippet.title: Wreckfest - PlayStation 5 Feature Trailer | PS5
snippet.description:
60 FPS. 4K Resolution. Faster Loading Times. Enhanced Lighting. Improved Visual Effects. 24 Player Multiplayer. Controller Haptic Feedback.

Current gen improvements are coming to Wreckfest.
Wreckfest is coming to PlayStation 5 on June 1st, 2021.

Owners of Wreckfest on PS4 can upgrade to the enhanced version on PS5 for $9.99 / € 9.99.
---
Website: https://order.wreckfestgame.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/wreckfest

#Wreckfest #DriveHardDieLast
